description:
The second collection of Handsome Flappy x Steinschleudi

From a total of 30 Steinschleudi's you get here the opportunity to be one of the first.
Since there are only 10 pieces per collection, the number per buyer is limited to 1 NFT.
When you buy this Handsome Steinschleudi NFT, you can mint 1 Handsome Flappy from collection #11-20 for free.

You can find the whole roadmap on my Homepage https://HandsomeFlappy.com

Within less than a month we have already collected over 900 Mi for a good cause. 
Be a part of the community and support non-profit organizations at the same time.

Have a great day, Hanna
name: Handsome Flappy x Steinschleudi #11-20
